-- U.S. weighs AIG conservatorship: Bloomberg
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2008 8:14pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/17/us-aig-conservatorship-idUSN1618037620080917

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. authorities were considering conservatorship as an option for insurer American International Group Inc., Bloomberg reported on Tuesday, citing two people briefed on the negotiations. 

 Additional details were not immediately available. A spokesperson for AIG was not immediately available.